What is Sorority life really like?!? Read on...
Watch REAL sorority hazing submissions from colleges across the country. See all the crazy shit these pledges will suffer through to earn the right to get in! All submissions are real. This shit is too good for us to make up!. Best of all we award the best sorority submission with a $10,000 cash prize to keep it interesting ;)
It's impossible to keep up with how much porn is out there! haha  Thanks!
